Developer Terms of Use
des:
"Unofficial Taylor Swift Quiz" is an Alexa skill designed to test your knowledge about one of the most popular pop singer. Users are asked general questions about her and must answer with a "yes" or "no." Each time the user guesses the answer, they earn one point. Every ten questions the user's point will be announced.
The multiplayer mode supports up to two players.
In the multiplayer mode each 20 questions will reveal the players' scores.
